                answer: "Kc = 2.96 molвҒ»ВІ dmвҒ¶; equilibrium is moderate, not strongly product-favoured at 500 K.",
                commonError: "Using stoichiometric coefficients as subscripts on concentration brackets rather than as powers. [NHвӮғ]ВІ means the concentration of NHвӮғ raised to the power 2 вҖ” it does NOT mean twice the concentration of NHвӮғ."
