                commonUse:    "Determination of oxidising agents (e.g. CuВІвҒә, ClвӮӮ, IOвӮғвҒ») вҖ” the oxidising agent first liberates IвӮӮ from excess KI; the IвӮӮ is then titrated with thiosulfate (an indirect method)"
