            "Environmental chemistry: dissolution of COвӮӮ in ocean water (COвӮӮ + HвӮӮO вҮҢ HвӮӮCOвӮғ вҮҢ HвҒә + HCOвӮғвҒ») is an equilibrium that drives ocean acidification",
