        question: "Pentane (CвӮ…HвӮҒвӮӮ) and 2,2-dimethylpropane (CвӮ…HвӮҒвӮӮ) are both alkanes with molecular formula CвӮ…HвӮҒвӮӮ. Pentane boils at 36В°C; 2,2-dimethylpropane boils at 9.5В°C. Explain the difference.",
