        "pH of a base = вҲ’log[OHвҒ»] вҖ” FALSE: this gives pOH, not pH; always convert using Kw: [HвҒә] = Kw/[OHвҒ»], then pH = вҲ’log[HвҒә]; alternatively pH = 14 вҲ’ pOH (at 25В°C only)",
