        "A solution with pH 4 is twice as acidic as a solution with pH 8 вҖ” FALSE: pH is a logarithmic scale; pH 4 has [HвҒә] = 10вҒ»вҒҙ; pH 8 has [HвҒә] = 10вҒ»вҒё; the ratio is 10вҒ»вҒҙ/10вҒ»вҒё = 10,000 вҖ” not 2"
