        "Adding water to a buffer significantly changes its pH вҖ” FALSE: dilution changes [HA] and [AвҒ»] proportionally, so the ratio [AвҒ»]/[HA] is unchanged; by HendersonвҖ“Hasselbalch, pH = pKa + log(ratio) is therefore unchanged on dilution (though capacity is reduced)"
