                    "3. О”GВ° = 180.5 вҲ’ (298)(0.0249) = 180.5 вҲ’ 7.42 = +173.1 kJ molвҒ»В№",
                    "Interpretation: О”GВ° > 0 вҶ’ non-spontaneous at 298 K; K << 1 (explains why atmosphere is not NO)"
