                    "2. Skeleton: S centre, 4 O atoms connected by single bonds (8 eвҒ» used)",
                    "3. Complete O octets: 4Г—6 = 24 eвҒ» as lone pairs; total used = 32 вң“",
                    "4. FC(S) = 6 вҲ’ 0 вҲ’ 4 = +2; FC(O) each = 6 вҲ’ 6 вҲ’ 1 = вҲ’1; sum = +2+4(вҲ’1) = вҲ’2 вң“",
                    "5. Minimise FC: convert 2 lone pairs on 2 O atoms to S=O double bonds",
                    "   New FC(S) = 6 вҲ’ 0 вҲ’ 6 = 0; double-bonded O: FC = 6вҲ’4вҲ’2 = 0; single-bonded O: FC = вҲ’1",
                    "   Sum still = вҲ’2 вң“; better вҖ” lower formal charges",
                    "Result: Best structure has 2 S=O and 2 SвҲ’O bonds (or resonance hybrid of 4 equivalent structures)"
