                    "4. 2 remaining вҶ’ lone pair on central O",
                    "5. Central O has 6 electrons вҖ” form double bond to one terminal O",
                    "6. Structure 1: O=OвҲ’O (double to left) ; Structure 2: OвҲ’O=O (double to right)",
                    "7. Both valid вҶ” ozone is the resonance hybrid",
                    "8. Bond order: 3 bonds in 2 structures over 2 OвҲ’O positions = 3/2 = 1.5",
