                    "2. Skeleton: P centre, 5 Cl atoms (5 bonds = 10 eвҒ» used)",
                    "3. Complete Cl octets: 5Г—6 = 30 eвҒ»; total used = 40 вң“",
                    "4. P has 5 bonding pairs = 10 electrons around P",
                    "5. P is in Period 3 вҶ’ has 3d orbitals вҶ’ can expand octet вң“",
                    "6. FC(P) = 5 вҲ’ 0 вҲ’ 5 = 0; FC(Cl) each = 7 вҲ’ 6 вҲ’ 1 = 0 вҖ” excellent formal charges",
